Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: Conveniently situated in the Naperville Office Park.  Easy access to two 4-way interchanges for East-West Tollway (I-88). Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Building has heated underground parking.  Parking is expandable to greater than 4 per 1000 square feet.  3-story atrium lobby clad in rich granite.  Conference facilities available.  Deli serving breakfast and lunch.  24-hour card key access.  Two sources of fiber optics and other state-of-the-art technology.
